{"tid":1482220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「落雨不去維園了」","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:42:50.000Z","uid":85385,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c4adc00cbf7115f1f46d195e035ab97a9754a6cd","tid":1482220,"uid":85385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:29:36.000Z","msg":"落雨就唔去？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">落雪</span></span>都照去呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一陣見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"53d4cd45a378a3f92098e4836f48eda250f5fd5e","tid":1482220,"uid":34970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:30:11.000Z","msg":"地震都去呀屌"},{"pid":"bbda26dfb76c53198a7f35c97469744087636622","tid":1482220,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:30:32.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"e510a478da086f8038d668942f86d0807e75c2ff","tid":1482220,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:30:47.000Z","msg":"催淚彈 布袋彈 橡膠彈<br />\n都唔怕"},{"pid":"6524c9ee41911c1165c8ec53eef83691cd640aec","tid":1482220,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:31:00.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=9245c40a\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=9245c40a\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"aa68607fa653097005aa22ae630755fd7547683d","tid":1482220,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:31:34.000Z","msg":"落大雨, 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7771f6c6d887056f1147a51a1514512cf20a0f6a","tid":1482220,"uid":85385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa68607fa653097005aa22ae630755fd7547683d","tid":1482220,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"